Jason Rumley
Director










Jason Rumley
Director





	Why did you choose Radian?

	One of the primary reasons I joined Radian is that I aspired to be part of a company that would leverage my more than 20 years of industry experience to influence change. Radian has been the perfect fit and continues to leverage my previous experience while strengthening my industry knowledge and business management skills even more.

	What do you most enjoy about what you do?

I enjoy the culture that Radian has developed and how it applies directly to our approach with our clients. This empowers all of us to leverage our strengths and challenges us in new areas of growth.       

	What are your passions outside of work?

My hobbies evolve around being outdoors as much as I can and include travel, camping, golf and photography.          

	What advice would you give new hires?

	Be open minded and ready to leverage your knowledge and experience within a team-led environment. Get ready to be challenged each and everyday!

	What has been your favorite moment at Radian?

	My favorite moment was after about six months of joining Radian, when I began to see our client’s performance be driven by the work I was part of developing and implementing.  At this point, I knew I had joined the company that best fit my interests and future career path.

	 

	To learn more about Radian email me at JRumley@radiangroup.com








