Robert Norris
Senior Manager










Robert Norris
Senior Manager





	Why did you choose Radian?

	Radian gave me the ability to be a part of a terrific, diverse team of professionals and to use my experience and skills to drive change and results with our clients.

	What do you most enjoy about what you do?

	Gaining the respect and trust of the clients. I enjoy becoming a trusted advisor and resource.

	What are your passions outside of work?

	Family. My six-year old daughter keeps me busy when I am home.  We also love the outdoors, camping and fishing in the summer, and skiing in the winter.

	What advice would you give new hires?

	Forge relationships within the firm. Because of the diversity of backgrounds and experience within Radian, there are so many excellent opportunities to grow professionally through these interactions.

	What has been your favorite moment at Radian?

	There are so many that can't be put down on permanent record (based on the advice of my attorney). My real answer: Every time we have a new engagement with a client, I reach that point where I realize the client sees us as a critical part of their team. That is job satisfaction.

	 

	To learn more about Radian email me at RNorris@radiangroup.com








