Kristin Caffey
Senior Director










Kristin Caffey
Senior Director





	Why did you choose Radian?

	First and foremost, I was attracted to the work. It's challenging and interesting; you're always learning something! Outside of wanting to get experience within a smaller company, the balance I can have between my personal and professional life really resonated with me. I am very passionate about my work and will always give 110%, but my life outside of work is equally important.   

	What do you most enjoy about what you do?

	I enjoy helping people connect the dots. The moment you see the clients “get it” and their eyes light up makes all the data mining worth it. It's rewarding to see them excited and learning.        

	What are your passions outside of work?

	I enjoy being active outdoors, doing yoga, shopping and, most importantly, spending time with my family!           

	What advice would you give new hires?

	My advice would be to take time to get to know the team and build relationships early. 

	What has been your favorite moment at Radian?

	It's hard to isolate one memory. I've really enjoyed the people, the work and the opportunity to grow as an individual.

	 

	To learn more about Radian email me at KCaffey@radiangroup.com








